Hallowell's Premium Double-Tier Three-Wide Lockers provide plenty of secure and durable storage, making them an excellent addition to your school hallways. Each locker features highly durable 16-gauge steel doors that come with louvers for ventilation. Hang backpacks and jackets on the one double-prong ceiling hook and two single hooks inside each locker. The stainless steel recessed handles won't scratch passersby and prevent the finish from being marred by a padlock (not included). Includes 6" high legs. Hallowell's Premium Double-Tier Three-Wide Lockers are made in the USA and GREENGUARD certified. Backed by a two-year warranty. $264.95 - $529.95
